<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA37">
<l>avaṟkaṭimaip paṭṭē ṉakattāṉ puṟattā</l>
<l>ṉuvarkkuṅ karuṅkaṭaṉī ruḷḷāṉ – ṟuvarkkum</l>
<l>pavaḷavāyp pūmakaḷum paṉmaṇippū ṇāran</l>
<l>tikaḻun tirumārpaṉ ṟāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In servitude to him I fell: he who is inside, who is outside,</l>
<l>he who is in the water of the salty black sea, the very one on whose</l>
<l>holy chest glitters an ornamented necklace with many jewels,</l>
<l>and the Lady of the flower with a mouth [like] red coral.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
